Expand card roster + rebirth-exclusive reward cards

- CardCatalog: ~26 new parody-star cards (transformative pun names only, no real
  players) across all rarities/positions ? roughly doubles the collection.
- 5 rebirth-EXCLUSIVE Mythic cards (The Prestige, Golden Reaper, The Ascended One,
